Luxury Italian Design in Dubai
Tonino Lamborghini Residences, developed by Gulf Land Property Developers, is a prestigious new development located in the Meydan area of Dubai. This luxurious complex comprises four towers, offering a selection of 541 residential units, including 1 to 4-bedroom apartments. Each residence showcases exquisite design elements from the renowned Italian Tonino Lamborghini Group, featuring high-quality materials, bespoke interiors, and elegantly crafted kitchens.
Prime Location and Connectivity
Situated in the upscale Meydan area, Tonino Lamborghini Residences offer residents easy access to key destinations in Dubai. The development is just 14 minutes from Downtown Dubai, 26 minutes from Dubai Marina, 14 minutes from DXB Airport, and 35 minutes from DWC Airport. This prime location ensures that residents can enjoy both the tranquility of Meydan and the vibrant lifestyle of Dubais bustling city center.
Amenities and Features
Residents of Tonino Lamborghini Residences will enjoy a range of luxurious amenities designed to enhance their living experience:

Exquisite Interiors: Apartments adorned with high-quality materials and furnishings, designed by Tonino Lamborghini's studios.
Prime Location: Close proximity to Downtown Dubai, Dubai Marina, and major airports.
Luxurious Living: A serene ambiance combined with sophisticated design elements.
Flexible Payment Plan: 70/30 payment plan to facilitate a smooth financial investment.

Flexible Payment Plan
To ease the financial investment, Tonino Lamborghini Residences offers a flexible 70/30 payment plan:

20% on Booking
50% during Construction
30% on Handover

Scheduled Handover
The expected handover for Tonino Lamborghini Residences is set for Q1 2027, ensuring timely completion and delivery of these luxurious apartments.
Handover Process


Notification:

As the handover date approaches, Gulf Land Property Developers will notify residents, providing detailed information on the handover process and required documentation.



Final Inspection:

A final inspection will be arranged for residents to review their new apartments and ensure that all specifications meet their expectations.



Payment of Final Installment:

The final 30% payment must be completed before the handover of the keys.



Handover Appointment:

Residents will receive the keys, access cards, and essential information during the scheduled handover appointment.



Move-In and Settling:

Residents can start moving into their new homes and enjoy the luxurious lifestyle offered by Tonino Lamborghini Residences.



Conclusion
Tonino Lamborghini Residences in Meydan, Dubai, offers an unparalleled living experience with its luxurious apartments and exquisite Italian design. Developed by Gulf Land Property Developers, this prestigious project provides a blend of sophistication and tranquility, making it an ideal choice for discerning homeowners. With a flexible 70/30 payment plan and scheduled handover in Q1 2027, Tonino Lamborghini Residences is set to redefine luxury living in Dubai.

This development aims to cater to families and individuals looking for contemporary living spaces with access to an array of amenities. With its strategic location, Luxury Family Residence allows for easy connectivity to major highways, schools, and popular destinations, making it an attractive choice for both residents and investors.
Key Features:

Spacious Living Spaces: The residences are designed with modern aesthetics and spacious layouts, making them suitable for family living while ensuring a stylish atmosphere.
Family-Oriented Amenities: Residents have access to a community with parks, playgrounds, and nearby schools, creating a family-friendly environment.
Convenient Location: Situated in JVC, the development offers proximity to key locations in Dubai, including major highways, the Dubai International Airport, and Jumeirah Beach.
Investment Potential: JVC is a popular area for rental and investment, offering a mix of high rental yields and potential for capital appreciation, making this property an appealing option for investors.

Luxury Family Residence in JVC brings together the best of family living with contemporary conveniences, presenting a well-rounded lifestyle that caters to modern needs.

Creek Island embodies a luxurious waterfront concept, blending upscale residences with captivating leisure and recreational facilities, crafting a premier waterfront community. Anchored by a verdant central park, a magnificent marina, an exclusive yacht club, and opulent five-star hotels, it offers residents unparalleled vistas and a one-of-a-kind living experience. 
Now comes the Creek Crescent, a sophisticated residential marvel soaring 22 stories high, complemented by a distinguished 4-story podium of world-class amenities. Nestled along is the picturesque view of both the marina, the skyline, and the city. With meticulous attention to detail, both the tower and podium are strategically positioned to capture the breathtaking vistas of Dubai Creek.
Beyond its private confines, Creek Crescent offers a realm of unparalleled recreational indulgence. The exclusive 4-story podium serves as a resident-only sanctuary, promising endless hours of tranquility. A harmonious blend of custom services and exquisite facilities awaits, featuring sumptuous swimming pools, a state-of-the-art gymnasium, outdoor play zones for children, inviting BBQ pits, and verdant lawns seamlessly integrated within the lush podium landscaping.
Creek Crescent promises a lifestyle like no other.

Chic Tower by de GRISOGONO, situated in the heart of Business Bay, Dubai, is an exquisite residential development by DAMAC Properties. This towering masterpiece is set to redefine luxury living with its holistic lifestyle experience, stunning architecture, and exceptional amenities.
Luxurious Living Spaces
The tower offers an exclusive selection of living spaces designed to cater to a diverse range of residents. These include:
Studio Apartments
The project provides elegant and thoughtfully designed studio apartments, offering a blend of comfort and functionality. Each unit is crafted to maximize space utilization while maintaining an aura of sophistication.
1-2 Bedroom Apartments
For those seeking a bit more space, the 1-2 bedroom apartments present a harmonious balance between luxury and practicality. These units offer ample room for relaxation and creative living arrangements.
Super Luxury 3-4 Bedroom Units
Adding an element of opulence, the tower showcases super luxury units with 3-4 bedrooms. These residences exude grandeur and come complete with terraces adorned with flowers and plants, an infinity pool, and a personal gym.
Wellness-Inspired Amenities
DAMAC Chic Tower stands out with its array of amenities designed to offer residents a holistic and rejuvenating lifestyle:
Revitalizing Baths
The tower boasts 7 revitalizing baths, meticulously crafted to promote detoxification and enhance skin radiance. These baths offer a unique blend of luxury and wellness, creating a spa-like experience within the confines of your home.
Spa and Outdoor Gym
Residents have the privilege of indulging in the main spa, which seamlessly extends into an outdoor gym. The gym features state-of-the-art equipment tailored for calisthenic-focused workouts, ensuring a comprehensive fitness regime.
Prime Location and Infrastructure
Strategically located in the main business hub of Business Bay, the development enjoys a privileged setting:
Proximity to Landmarks
Chic Tower faces the prestigious Oberoi Hotel and is adjacent to the iconic Opus building, adding an element of exclusivity. It's conveniently situated near Al Mustaqbal Street, Sheikh Zayed Road, and Burj Khalifa Boulevard, making it easy to access key areas of the city.
Surrounding Infrastructure
The tower is enveloped by a wealth of essential infrastructure within walking distance. From fitness centers like Full Circle EMS Fitness Center to supermarkets like W Mart and Spinneys, and even banking services from Dubai Islamic Bank, every convenience is at your doorstep.
Investment Potential
Chic Tower isn't just a luxurious residence; it's a prime investment opportunity:
Attractive Rental Potential
With similar projects in Business Bay commanding a starting rental price of AED 80,000 per year for a 1-bedroom apartment, Chic Tower presents an estimated ROI of 8%, making it an enticing prospect for investors.
Investor Visa Opportunities
Investors can capitalize on the chance to purchase an entire floor within the tower. As construction progresses, the property's value is expected to rise. Additionally, property owners may be eligible to apply for a 3-year investor visa or a 5-year UAE Golden visa based on the property's value.
Chic Tower stands as a testament to luxury, wellness, and investment potential, offering a unique living experience that blends residential opulence with a holistic approach to well-being.

MESMERISING VIEWSSoak in the different sides of Dubai with stunning panoramic views. From the shimmering lights of Bluewaters reflecting off the water to the bright lights of JBR adorning the sky, to the open expanse of the Gulf - there's a view for every outlook.

SEAVIEWSSoak in the gentle movements of water as they create living and breathing light patterns that evoke a sense of solace. Enjoy the rising sun spill over the horizon at dawn and watch yachts dot the coastline by day. And at dusk indulge in unforgettable shades of light as the dimming sun nestles into the waters of the Gulf.
CITYSCAPESDay or night, the citys skyline will take your breath away. Breathe in  the splendor of the architecture the city has to offer. Watch the morning fog gently envelop all the buildings and the twinkling of the night lights as you gaze at the cityscape.
AMENITIESA community that boasts a wide range of amenities, exclusive to all our residents, that reinvigorate both body and mind. From world-class exercise and meditation facilities, to pools with a view, to secure family spaces, indulge in facilities deserving of the Bluewaters brand.
CONTEMPORARY STYLINGWhere land meets sea. Bluewaters Bay is a place where open-plan apartment layouts and contemporary styling offer a true sense of grandeur. At the heart of Bluewaters Bay lies a philosophy that has inspired furnishing and spaces - all styled and designed to evoke calm, sanctuary and comfort.
MODERN DESIGNHomes that are defined by subtle elegance and a sophisticated finish. With Miami living as our architect's muse, floor to ceiling glass allows light to flood into living spaces. All facets of this development have been designed to provide everything you could possibly need for a truly exceptional living experience.
URBAN HAVENLuxuriate in vast open spaces that let you discover your best self. Discover pathways that lead to serene nature and glitzy cityscapes.
BEACHFRONT LIVINGTake solace in soft, inviting white sands as you stroll on idyllic beaches. Dip your toes in the tranquility of the ocean as you find a new sense of calm. Watch the sea glisten as you dive into the aquamarine sea. Experience life by the beach like no other.
LUXURIOUS LIFESTYLEWalk along a vibrant tapestry of busy boulevards filled with bustling restaurants where you can indulge in your favorite dishes. Turn the corner and find tranquil spaces where you can soak in natural landscapes enveloped by the vastness of the Arabian Sea.
LIVING SPACESDesigned to let the inside-out and the outside-in, all of our interior living spaces have been inspired by a lifestyle thats in perfect harmony with the surrounding world. Quite simply, these are spaces for mind and body best enjoyed with family and friends.

From open-plan, modern kitchens, to bedrooms with dreamy views. Here, you can experience open living in apartments that invite tranquility and vibrancy inside.

Discover LIV LUX, an exclusive luxury residential development poised to grace the vibrant landscape of Dubai Marina. Situated on one of the last remaining plots in this bustling district, this waterfront masterpiece is set to stand tall with its 47 floors. Offering an array of sophisticated living spaces, LIV LUX by LIV Developers is destined to become the crown jewel of Dubai Marina.
Unveiling the Residences
Step into a world of refined living as LIV LUX presents a diverse range of premium living spaces. Choose from exquisite 1 to 2-bedroom apartments that exude elegance, or immerse yourself in the opulence of 2 to 4-bedroom signature apartments. For those seeking ultimate comfort and privacy, our 4-bedroom duplex penthouses and 5-bedroom duplex superlux penthouses await. These penthouses redefine luxury, boasting private infinity pools, serene zen gardens, private massage areas, sun-lounging spaces, and more.
A Symphony of Luxury
LIV LUX residences are meticulously designed to offer the epitome of comfort and style. Bedrooms feature well-curated wardrobes and ample storage. The kitchens are adorned with appliances from renowned European brands such as Siemens, Miele, and Villeroy & Boch. Bathed in natural light, these residences offer panoramic views through expansive windows enhanced by the minimum 3-meter ceiling height. Step onto the fantastic open-air balconies and soak in breathtaking vistas of Dubai Marina, the Arabian Gulf, and the iconic Palm Jumeirah.
Unparalleled Location
Nestled between the crystal-clear waters of the Gulf and the vibrant Dubai Marina, LIV LUX enjoys a prime location. A mere 20-minute journey will transport you to Downtown Dubai, while Dubai Airport (DXB) is conveniently reachable in under 20 minutes.
Retail and Entertainment Delights
Retail therapy and entertainment are never far away. Dubai Marina Mall beckons with its 140 retail stores and a tempting array of 21 dining options. Meanwhile, Nakheel Mall on Palm Jumeirah offers 140 boutiques, 30 cafes and restaurants, as well as exciting attractions like VOX Cinemas, Fabyland, and Trampo Extreme.
Unmissable Family Experiences
For families, LIV LUX offers proximity to exceptional attractions. The world's largest observation wheel, Ain Dubai, located on Bluewaters Island, sets the stage for unforgettable events. The Aquaventure Waterpark with its thrilling slides, Shark Safari, and Shark Snorkeling, along with The Lost Chambers Aquarium, promises captivating experiences for both young and old.
Embrace the Extraordinary
Choosing to make LIV LUX your home means embracing a life of opulent waterfront living coupled with five-star amenities. Experience a grand arrival through the stunning drop-off, enhanced by 24/7 valet service. The expansive lobby, adorned with a welcoming reception and attentive concierge services, sets the tone for a lavish lifestyle.
Furthermore, owning a residence at LIV LUX isn't just about luxury living; it's also a savvy investment. According to Property Finder, the average ROI for 1-bedroom residences in Dubai Marina stands at an impressive 7.14%. Make the right choice by becoming a part of LIV LUX, where luxury knows no bounds.

Sobha Seahaven is a luxurious waterfront development located in the Mouth of Dubai Harbour. It is being developed by Sobha Realty, a premium property developer known for luxurious developments such as Crest Grande, The Waves, Hartland Greens and One Park Avenue.
The development will consist of three towers overlooking Dubai Marina and the Arabian Gulf. The dynamic architecture will be inspired by luxury yachts, the wind and the sea.
Units

Sobha Seahaven will offer a wide range of world-class amenities, including:

Infinity pool
Sports facilities, including a zone for yoga, aerobics, a skate park, and a health club
Sauna and steam rooms
Valet and concierge services
Pet-friendly zone
Retail and dining options

Sobha Seahaven is a unique development that offers a number of advantages over other waterfront developments in Dubai. Here are just a few reasons why you should choose Sobha Seahaven:

Prime location: Sobha Seahaven is located in the Mouth of Dubai Harbour, which is one of the most desirable locations in Dubai. It is close to all of the major attractions and landmarks, as well as to Sheikh Zayed Road, which provides easy access to other areas of the city.
Luxurious apartments: The apartments at Sobha Seahaven are designed to the highest standards and feature premium finishes and appliances. Smart home system and state-of-the-art home appliances will also be featured in Sobha Seahaven.
World-class amenities: Sobha Seahaven offers a wide range of world-class amenities, including an infinity pool, sports facilities, sauna and steam rooms, valet and concierge services, and a pet-friendly zone.
Golden Visa eligibility: Purchasing a residential unit at Sobha Seahaven makes you eligible to apply for a ten year Golden UAE Visa.

Unrivaled Location and Unforgettable Experiences

Nautical Chic Meets Modern Luxury
Step inside and discover a world of refined elegance. Each residence features a nautical color palette rich in deep blues and crisp whites, complemented by impeccable textures and finishes. Natural light bathes the exquisite elements, showcasing panoramic sea and cityscapes.
 
Effortless Living Awaits
Dubai Harbour Residences elevates the beachfront experience with an array of amenities designed for effortless living.
From rooftop infinity pools with sweeping vistas to a fitness center, wellness facilities, dedicated family spaces, and separate children's areas, there's something for everyone. This exclusive collection caters to life's many needs and moments, allowing residents to thrive in their luxurious sanctuary.

The tower features an exquisite collection of studio to four-bedroom apartments and opulent duplexes, each offering floor-to-ceiling windows, high-end interiors, and panoramic views of landmarks such as the Burj Khalifa and Dubai Water Canal. With a focus on quality, innovation, and functionality, every unit reflects Binghattis signature fusion of art and design.
Residents of One Downtown will enjoy access to a host of lifestyle amenities, including rooftop pools, state-of-the-art fitness centers, wellness zones, children's play areas, and fine retail spaces within the development. Its strategic location ensures unparalleled convenience, with Dubai Mall, financial districts, and cultural venues just minutes away.

Waada  Cascada 1 is the inaugural jewel of the Waada master development by BT Properties, introducing a new chapter of refined, nature-integrated living in Dubai South. Inspired by the vision of seamless harmony between community, comfort, and sustainability, Cascada 1 delivers a lifestyle that is modern yet grounded in human connection and green urbanism.

What Makes It Unique
1. A Legacy Transformed for Dubai
Backed by the pioneering vision of Bahria Town, Cascada 1 represents the groups first bold step into the UAE market. While Bahrias legacy is rooted in Pakistans largest gated communities, Cascada 1 adapts that DNA to Dubais global standardswith smarter infrastructure, sustainable materials, and a people-first design philosophy.
2. A Verdant Urban Oasis
With over 40% of the Waada community dedicated to green corridors, rooftop gardens, and cascading water features, Cascada 1 transforms the idea of vertical living. Unlike conventional towers, this G+16 building is immersed in a larger ecosystem of walkable boulevards, landscaped meditative spaces, and wellness-centric zones.
3. Curated Interiors, Tailored for Life
Each unit, whether a 1, 2, or 3-bedroom apartment, is crafted not just for aestheticsbut for living well. Expect spacious layouts, natural light-maximizing windows, closed kitchens with clean finishes, and thoughtful additions like powder rooms and maids quarters. Every detail is attuned to both family needs and modern tastes.
4. Long-Term Value in a High-Growth District
Cascada 1 sits at the gateway to Expo City and the Al Maktoum Airport corridor, aligning with Dubais long-term growth blueprint (2040 Urban Master Plan). The area is rapidly becoming a magnet for businesses, logistics, and tourismmaking this a prime address for both end-users and investors.

Every line, space, and surface at Gate Eleven is purposefully designed. The residence merges minimalistic design with functional elegance to deliver:

Bright, open-plan apartments with clean lines and natural light
Organic textures and modern finishes for timeless appeal
Balconies and terraces overlooking landscaped zones

This is living with claritywhere aesthetics support lifestyle.

Wide tree-lined avenues and open green parks
World-class schools, sports facilities, and wellness centers
Access to high-end retail and dining at Meydan One and beyond

Its the ideal home base for families and professionals who want room to grow, yet remain intimately close to the citys energy.

Unmatched Accessibility
Strategically positioned in District 11, Gate Eleven offers swift access to Dubais key districts:

10 minutes to Downtown Dubai
12 minutes to Business Bay
15 minutes to Dubai International Airport
Direct connectivity to Al Khail Road and Sheikh Zayed Road

From morning meetings to evening walks, your entire day unfolds seamlessly.

The Smarter Choice for Living or Leasing

SAAS Hills by SAAS Properties is set to transform Dubai Science Park with its striking blend of contemporary elegance and natural inspiration. The development features two architecturally stunning towers, their curved silhouettes inspired by the flowing contours of desert rocks, creating a refreshing and organic aesthetic rarely seen in urban Dubai.
This thoughtfully planned community offers a wide array of residencesfrom cozy studios and modern one to three-bedroom apartments to luxurious duplex townhouses and sky villasdesigned to suit every preference and lifestyle. With 857 homes in total, SAAS Hills invites residents to experience a harmonious fusion of space, style, and comfort.
What truly distinguishes SAAS Hills is its focus on health and innovation. Incorporating advanced VLED technology from Vortex Biotech, each residence ensures cleaner air quality by actively combating viruses and allergens, promoting a safer and more comfortable living environment.
Beyond the homes, the project offers extensive amenities spanning over 16,000 sq. ft., including swimming pools, wellness centers, sports courts, a cinema, and retail outlets, all crafted to support a vibrant and balanced lifestyle. Situated minutes away from Dubais key landmarks and business hubs, SAAS Hills combines prime connectivity with the tranquility of Dubai Science Park.
With flexible payment options and a completion target by late 2027, SAAS Hills presents a unique opportunity to invest in a sustainable, tech-forward community designed for the future of urban living.

Whether you're a young couple, a growing family, or an investor, Rosehill offers a lifestyle that feels both relaxed and upscale.
